node.text:
The truth is most people don’t work that hard 🤷🏻‍♀️

I was a natural food chef, I had a business called Bethenny Bakes and another one called Princess Pashmina, all while I was broke. I was constantly thinking about ways to be successful and how to execute on my ideas. If you are a true entrepreneur, it’s very challenging to turn it off.

I share a lot of my business tips on my @justbwithbethenny podcast. 🎙I also talk to people who started from the bottom and now they are at the top. Who would you like to see me interview next? 🎧

I always go beyond the surface on the @justbwithbethenny podcast and I was thrilled to talk honestly with the COO of Facebook @sherylsandberg. She propelled the platform to the $1 trillion valuation it is today.🙌

Sheryl shared her "aha moment" when organizing Facebook, her experience beating gender bias in business and how losing her husband changed her. 

Listen and follow Just B with Bethenny Frankel on the iHeartRadio App, Apple Podcasts or wherever you get your podcasts.🎙

THE B IS BACK ON A WHOLE NEW LEVEL 🙌 and this time it’s #JUSTB

I’m humbled by the response and the incredible guests who have chosen to spend their time talking to me and sharing with YOU what they have learned along the way.  This podcast is the key to a toolbox to your business success in a non traditional way. 

You don’t want to miss my first guest on iHeart — @officiallymcconaughey! He shares how he found the courage to break out and go his own way. This was his #greenlight. 

Listen to Just B with Bethenny Frankel on the iHeartRadio App, Apple Podcasts or wherever you get your podcasts.🎙

Smart Salads with Bethenny 🥗

Here are my favorite tips for creating a salad ⬇️

1. Avoid already chopped greens because they perish and brown quickly. 🥬
2. Find a firm, but not hard, avocado (not as soft as my tush).🥑
3. Buy small grape tomatoes that will keep longer in your fridge. (People don’t refrigerate tomatoes to preserve flavor but I do).🍅
4. Use pre boiled bagged eggs. I use the whole egg. 🥚
5. Salt and pepper your greens before dressing them with @skinnygirlbrand.🧂

You may have seen this clip on my show @thebigshotonmax. We did the avocado tush test in the latest episode. What should I make next?

node.text:
Talk about a transformation 💁🏻‍♀️

I totally renovated this Greenwich, CT home from being outdated and boring to a private, serene retreat. The open concept of the home features walls of windows, vaulted ceilings and indoor-outdoor living. 

The views of the pond from different locations in the house are incredible.💧 The primary bedroom has a luxurious spa-like bath featuring a soaking tub 🛁, boutique style dressing room and walk-in closet✨. 

We also resurfaced the pool and spa and rebuilt a clay tennis court.🎾 Designed in collaboration with Sorting House. More Bethenny Frankel Design projects to come.

I always go beyond the surface on the @justbwithbethenny podcast and I was thrilled to talk honestly with the COO of Facebook @sherylsandberg. She propelled the platform to the $1 trillion valuation it is today.🙌

Listen and follow Just B with Bethenny Frankel on the iHeartRadio App, Apple Podcasts or wherever you get your podcasts.🎙
